-- pip install 'molecule[docker]'
-- molecule init role <role name> --driver-name docker
now edit the main.yml in <rolename>/tasks/ and also add other tasks if needed
now edit the author name in -- vi meta/main.yml
now run -- molecule test -- to do end to end testing
if you want the container to stay after testing use command -- molecule converge
to go into the launcher conatiner use command - molecule login
to delete the conatiner use  -- molecule destroy

if you want to the change the os (centos, ubuntu ,fedora ) edit the image name in <rolename>/molecule/default/molecule.yml

